###########################
# Setup webtools_weeblefm #
###########################

$prefix = wherever webtools installed (e.g., /usr/lib64/webtools)

For weeblefm do the following steps:

0) Copy sample configuration file.
   $ cd $prefix/config
   $ cp weeblefm_config.php.sample weeblefm_config.php
   $ vi weeblefm_config.php

1) Copy sample settings configuration file.*
   $ cd $prefix/html
   $ cp settings.php.sample settings.php
   $ vi settings.php

2) Copy sample loginform configuration file.*
   $ cd $prefix/html
   $ cp loginform.html.sample loginform.html
   $ vi loginform.html

3) Done.

*Note: When configuring ftp_Servers remember to add corresponding servers to loginform.html select options
